channel.title: Fix Moparscape's item list?
channel.description: Hi. I am running mac OSX and the only client I know that actually works for it is Moparscape which I am running right now. And I am currently playing a server that has Java items on it. Is there anyway I can change moparscape's item list with the item list for that server. If so can someone show me how to? Or if not can someone make the client for the server a .jar file?
